{"tid":2158370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★首宗Bitcoin櫃員機漏洞騙案 3騙徒撳走$23萬","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:35:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3cfdf439a3a8e588063c9ff125ff6dd7aa444c8","tid":2158370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"3名男子伺準Bitcoin提款機的漏洞，在未經核實身份下多次成功提款，共計22.6萬元。警方經調查拘捕3名男子涉嫌串謀欺詐，今次是首次發現有人針對加密貨幣櫃員機的漏洞而進行的騙案。<br />\n<br />\n受害是兩間加密貨幣的機構，警方就櫃員機的漏洞，已經給予受害機構安全交易建議，他們會進行系統優化以堵塞漏洞。警方拒絕透露有關漏洞，但指一般而言，加密貨幣轉換時要證明和核實，而犯罪集團利用一些方法，在未經核實情況下提取款項。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200815/3BZHBKOEZ5HYPDSPNDXFSNY5BY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200815%2F3BZHBKOEZ5HYPDSPNDXFSNY5BY%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=1b21f00a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200815%2F3BZHBKOEZ5HYPDSPNDXFSNY5BY%2F&h=c35e07b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200815/3BZHBKOEZ5HYPDSPNDXFSNY5BY/</a>"},{"pid":"acd12d9b45d2ac33b703c3f1ac2df410d8a24651","tid":2158370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdba6e4ac18386026b43a6001a3a4d2305819ac","tid":2158370,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"咁神奇，副機公司自已做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5accd831583813dd02a6be300a7906a0fe9d5da9